    "We quantify the magnitude of both effects respectively.",
    "Third, we study if changes in users' tweeting activity originate from shifts between languages and quantify the magnitude of these shifts.",
    "Fourth and finally, we take a closer look at those users that switch from predominately tweeting in Russian to predominately tweeting in Ukrainian with the outbreak of the war.",
